Things to note:
----------------
   
1. In the ask/src/index.js , Under Message Intent, change the url to point to the right microservice

var url = "https://hook.io/vijayvikram11844/sendmessage?text=" + encodeURIComponent(message) + "&number=" + name + "&messagetype=" + messageType;

 
